.name
Zippy
.author
Michael Weiblen 
.version
2.5
.description
A "Graphical Shell".  Opens a medium-size window and attaches a menu-strip
for performing all sort of disk/data manipulations.  Features script files
allowing you to attach custom menu selections as you move between
directories.  Also included is an intuition based utility for altering
FileInfo data.  (filename, filenote, RWED attributes, etc.) 
